  <title>[RP] FST: Anju Tominaga &amp; Ma Ri Seoung</title>
  <link>http://unnamed-world.livejournal.com/5784.html</link>
  <description>&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: x-large; &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Georgia&quot;&gt;Ode To The Apricot&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Georgia&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Anju Tominaga &amp;amp; Seoung Ma Ri&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;cutid1&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Dance With My Father&lt;/em&gt; - Celine Dion&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;If I could get another chance&lt;br /&gt;Another walk, another dance with him&lt;br /&gt;I&apos;d play a song that would never ever end&lt;br /&gt;How I&apos;d love, love, love, to dance with my father again&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;When I and my mother will disagree&lt;br /&gt;To get my way I would run from her to him&lt;br /&gt;He&apos;d make me laugh just to comfort me&lt;br /&gt;Yeah, yeah, then finally make me do just what my mama says&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Later that night when I was asleep&lt;br /&gt;He left a dollar under my sheet&lt;br /&gt;Never dreamed that he would be gone from me&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The House That Built Me&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt; - Miranda Lambert&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;I thought if I could touch this place or feel it&lt;br /&gt;This brokenness inside me might start healing&lt;br /&gt;Out here it&amp;rsquo;s like I&amp;rsquo;m someone else&lt;br /&gt;I thought that maybe I could find myself&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If I could just come in I swear I&amp;rsquo;ll leave&lt;br /&gt;Won&amp;rsquo;t take nothing but a memory&lt;br /&gt;From the house that built me&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Colorful Days&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt; - Minami-ke&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;Tripping and looking up at the sky,&lt;br /&gt; I saw tomorrow&apos;s wind is blowing through it.&lt;br /&gt;No matter how many times, we can start. &lt;br /&gt;We&apos;ll turn our wishes into feathers, definitely.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Atlantis Princess&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt; -- BoA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;I dont ever let go again &lt;br /&gt;of my forgotten memories &lt;br /&gt;I hope I wont forget my small hopes and dreams &lt;br /&gt;I whisper that to the heavens&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where Do You Start?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt; - Barbra Streisand&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;em&gt;Which books are yours?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;em&gt;Which tapes and dreams belong to you and which are mine?&lt;br /&gt;Our lives are tangled like the branches of a vine that intertwine&lt;br /&gt;So many habits that we&apos;ll have to break&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Time After Time ~ Hana Mau Machi De ~&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt; - Kuraki Mai&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;			If I could have met you in the city of changing hues&lt;br /&gt;			I wouldn&apos;t need any more promises&lt;br /&gt;			More than anyone else you are so easy to hurt&lt;br /&gt;			I want to be with you--this time, forever.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a name=&apos;cutid1-end&apos;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
